The paper deals with the creation of rankings based on pairwise comparisons, which is a common problem in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of inconsistency indices is related to data analysis and decision-making, which are also relevant topics in data science (cs.DS) and social networks (cs.SI). Finally, the application of the modified indices in practice can be related to computational engineering (cs.CE).
